You can be wrong with the man.

550
00:44:42,464 --> 00:44:46,904
And then there's one more thing I want to tell you.

551
00:44:46,904 --> 00:44:47,324
help

552
00:45:16,504 --> 00:45:17,944
You'd better use your left arm.

553
00:45:20,504 --> 00:45:22,124
This will be my last story.

554
00:45:22,124 --> 00:45:23,724
She's famous now.

555
00:45:23,724 --> 00:45:26,164
No matter how difficult it is, you can't just abandon her.

556
00:45:27,034 --> 00:45:28,334
The doctor will give you an injection of morphine.

557
00:45:28,334 --> 00:45:29,794
The quantity is not much.

558
00:45:34,404 --> 00:45:35,684
Naran, I'm not good at all.

559
00:45:35,684 --> 00:45:36,864
Will you be able to handle it?

560
00:45:51,504 --> 00:45:55,764
I'm only worried about the wounds you've caused.

561
00:45:55,764 --> 00:45:56,704
Wow!

562
00:45:56,704 --> 00:45:59,644
I probably will never be able to forget.

563
00:46:01,314 --> 00:46:05,514
It hurts more than any time I've ever been sad.

564
00:46:05,864 --> 00:46:08,704
It was my own mistake to trust.

565
00:46:08,704 --> 00:46:12,254
and give it all to you with all my heart

566
00:46:12,254 --> 00:46:14,884
For the heart

567
00:46:14,884 --> 00:46:19,064
I found it because it was a late day.

568
00:46:19,064 --> 00:46:22,904
For the heart

569
00:46:22,904 --> 00:46:26,494
For the heart

570
00:46:32,244 --> 00:46:36,324
Make it one time
